text_block_list.text: When I was heading to the trainer's room with Matikanetannhauser——

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
Yes... since I woke up this morning...
Did I do something unhealthy, I wonder...

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Um... no issues with my recent sleep schedule.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
My exercise time hasn't changed much either,
and I'm eating my meals heartily...

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
——Oh, the air pressure is low today,
so that might be the cause.

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
Alright! To make the weather better,
I'll make a teru teru bozu when I get back to my room!

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text:
Teru teru teru, mun mun mu~n!
I want warm, sunny weather~!

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Ouch... my head hurts from singing...
Matikanetannhauser was troubled by a headache for a while.
